I play on Ay Ro... send me a /tell if you want
i play quite a few charcters but i been playing "Yummii" my new paladin the
most lately... i actually play 2 accounts at once, so Yummii will prolly
always be logged on when im on until shes 50+ :-) i use my cleric to PL her
and my wizard as a taxi for her. ok maybe i play too much :-)
